isionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IIIspc</date>
<placeName cert="high">Arsinoite</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>χαῖρε, κύριέ μου Ἑρμᾶ. 

    <lb n="2"/>καλῶς <choice><corr>ποιήσεις</corr><sic>ποιησις</sic></choice> μὴ ἀμελή-

    <lb n="3"/>σας ἀνελθεῖν ἔχων τὴν 

    <lb n="4"/>πρόσοδον καὶ τὰ τοῦ μέ-

    <lb n="5"/>τρου. ἀλλὰ καὶ δὸς τὰ ναῦ-

    <lb n="6"/>λα τῷ μέλλοντι αὐτὰ 

    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr>μεταφέρειν</corr><sic>μεταφεριν</sic></choice> ἐπὶ τὴν Φι-

    <lb n="8"/>λαγρίδα, ἀλλ᾽ ἵνα καὶ κω-

    <lb n="9"/>μάρχας ἀναδῶται καὶ 

    <lb n="10"/>περὶ <choice><corr>ὧν</corr><sic>των</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἀνηλώκατε</corr><sic>αναλωκαται</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>μάθηται πῶς <choice><corr>μέλλει</corr><sic>μελλι</sic></choice> ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="12"/>παραδέχεσθαι. ἤδη γὰρ κα-

    <lb n="13"/>τέλαβεν ὁ ἕτερος μηνιαῖος. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὐχόμεθα. </ab></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0268" notBefore="0249" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 249 - 268</date></p></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört wahrscheinlich zum Heroninos - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Flor.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">345</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">11172</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0111</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">345</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0111;3;345" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">74</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.11172" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>